Name: Vamprah
 Beast mode: Female Vampire

Special =
Power: "Banshee's Scream", a scream (Ultrasonic and not) that is able to di=
zzy and beat at his enemies or preys; its also can break glass and other th=
ings. She can heard ultrasonic sounds and see in the darkness better than o=
thers.

 Weapons: Laser gun. She has the skill to use all sort of weapons.
=

 Favorite Hobby: Drink blood of big mammals or the energy of her enemies.
=

 Behavior: Cool, smart and mercyless. she always try to reach her own goal=
s, in spite of circumstances. Her bright mind and fatal charming can help h=
er to destroy her enemies.

 Description: 

Her helmet reminds a Vampire's =
head, she could move her big ears and locate her preys whit them. Her helme=
t color is black, her oval face is silver-gray and her eyes have bright col=
or amber.

 Her armor reminds at Batgirl's design but more scared; it has s=
carce silver lines in; She has black shoulder plates in her shoulders and a=
 sort of belt in her waist. Her arms are silver and she has larges nails. H=
er build is sexy and athletic. Sometimes she covers her body with wings and=
 that makes her look her more sinister. Her body mixs silver-gray and black=
 parts.

 She seems use booths that end below her knees. In her transformat=
ion, Vampire beast's head disappears.

 Weakness: She hates the Sun. Vampra=
h's eyes can't stand a high light, its painful for her, due that she leaves=
 her hideout at sunset or at night.

Background:

Nobody knows a lot about =
Vamprah, rumours say several things about her: that she's an experiment of =
Tripedocus Council,  that she belongs to other transformer's race, etc.  Bu=
t anything is sure.
